## Description {#details}

An <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/json/array">Array</a> is a JSON array, which contains heterogeneous JSON values.

It simulates std::vector&lt;Value&gt;.

Definition at line 164 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/support/json-h">JSON.h</a>.
